{"title":"Mac 下避免 rm 引发的血案","date":"2018-04-12T13:53:11.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 12, 2018","L":"04/12/2018","MM-DD":"04-12"},"link":"2018/avoid-rm-induced-bloody-cases","comments":true,"tags":["rm"],"categories":["程序员必备"],"updated":"2022-09-02T06:38:13.683Z","content":"<p>习惯使用终端的用户，常会用 <code>rm -fr</code> 命令执行删除操作，但是这种删除的方式不会出现在废纸篓中，一旦误删，要想找回就比较麻烦。近期听说的此类血案也比较多，为了避免造成悲剧，推荐使用 trash 命令来执行删除。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"安装-trash\">安装 trash<a title=\"#安装-trash\" href=\"#安装-trash\"></a></h2>\n<p>通过 Homebrew 安装 <a href=\"https://github.com/ali-rantakari/trash\" target=\"_blank\">Trash</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">brew install trash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装成功后，可以通过 <code>trash -fr filename </code>命令删除文件，且文件会移到废纸篓中。</p>\n<h2 id=\"用-trash-替换-rm-命令\">用 trash 替换 rm 命令<a title=\"#用-trash-替换-rm-命令\" href=\"#用-trash-替换-rm-命令\"></a></h2>\n<p>打开 ~/.bash_profile 文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在文件中加入以下代码后保存文件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">alias</span> <span class=\"built_in\">rm</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;trash&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使命令生效：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这时执行 rm 命令，被删除的文件就会存放在废纸篓中了，废纸篓里的文件虽无法执行“放回原处”的方法，但可以通过鼠标拖拽恢复。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"App Store 审核经验","link":"2018/review-experience"},"next":{"title":"iOS 中 framework 和 bundle 的制作","link":"2018/making-frameworks-and-bundles"},"plink":"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/avoid-rm-induced-bloody-cases/","toc":[{"id":"安装-trash","title":"安装 trash","index":"1"},{"id":"用-trash-替换-rm-命令","title":"用 trash 替换 rm 命令","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"FiTeen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/avoid-rm-induced-bloody-cases/\" title=\"Mac 下避免 rm 引发的血案\">https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/avoid-rm-induced-bloody-cases/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}